{"ts":"2026-06-27T02:26:39.602Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Drafting the Form Structure**\n\nI've successfully finished writing and editing the layout and right column sandbox. I'm now focusing on drafting the left column form structure. The goal is to design a form that fits perfectly, replacing `REPLACE_ME_FORM`. I'm starting the initial draft process.\n\n\n**Designing the Form Structure**\n\nI am now focusing on designing the form's structure. I've begun drafting the code based on the layout, aiming for completeness and conciseness, all while adhering to the character limit. Currently, I'm focusing on the header and tab selection, working to build out each section with specific styling.\n\n\n**Refining Button Styling**\n\nI'm now refining the button styling within the form. I'm focusing on the visual cues for selected and unselected states. I'm tweaking the text color, border, and overall look to ensure a clear indication of the active authentication method.\n\n\n**Implementing Form Fields**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in implementing the form fields. The focus is on the enterprise email input, integrating state management and event handlers for a smooth user experience. I've designed a clear visual structure for the email input and now I'm thinking about conditional rendering of the password field based on the selected authentication method. I'm aiming for concise yet comprehensive code.\n\n\n**Adding Passphrase Functionality**\n\nI'm now integrating the passphrase key field and associated \"Forgot Key?\" functionality. I'm focusing on the visual design and interaction, including the input field, the visibility toggle, and the forgot key button. I'm also ensuring the field is properly linked to the state management for secure and efficient handling of the passphrase.\n\n\n**Adding Password Functionality**\n\nI'm now adding the password field and visibility toggle. I'm focusing on the visual design, state management, and interaction, including the input field and visibility toggle. My goal is a secure and user-friendly experience, ensuring a seamless flow within the authentication form.\n\n\n**Adding OTP Integration**\n\nI'm now integrating the one-time passcode (OTP) functionality. I'm focusing on the input field, the \"Trouble sending?\" button, and the alert message. My priority is to create a seamless user experience, including the prompt of filling in a 6-digit passcode to run in the local developer mode. I am now working on ensuring proper event handling and state management for the OTP input.\n\n\n**Refining Submit Button**\n\nI'm now refining the visual styling for the submit button. I'm focusing on hover and active states, including subtle shadow effects for added depth, ensuring a clear visual indication of interaction. I'm also addressing the error handling, crafting specific design elements that will be conditionally rendered, including the error message text.\n\n\n**Adding SSO Buttons**\n\nI'm now integrating SSO connectors into the form. I've added button placeholders with visual styling, including a separator and grid layout. I'm focusing on the \"SSO Connectors\" section, including visual elements and placeholder functionality for future SSO integrations.\n\n\n**Integrating SSO Buttons**\n\nI'm now integrating Microsoft Entra ID and Okta SSO connectors. I've designed and styled buttons with company logos, focusing on clear visual distinction. I'm focusing on the click handlers and user prompts, aiming for seamless SSO initiation. I'm working on the design and integrating the button text and icons.\n\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T02:26:39.605Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"alhmbgw8","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/portal/SecureLogin.tsx","old_text":"                REPLACE_ME_FORM","new_text":"                {/* Header row */}\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-zinc-800/40\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h2 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">Enclave Authorization</h2>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] text-zinc-500 mt-0.5\">Initialize cryptographic handshake protocols.</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-[8px] font-mono font-bold tracking-wider\">\n                    <span className=\"h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse\" />\n                    ONLINE\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Tab select */}\n                <div className=\"flex border-b border-zinc-800/60\" role=\"tablist\">\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => { setAuthMethod(\"credentials\"); setError(\"\"); }}\n                    className={`flex-1 pb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-b-2 transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n                      authMethod === \"credentials\"\n                        ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-white\"\n                        : \"border-transparent text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    Secure Keycard\n                  </button>\n                  <button\n                    type=\"button\"\n                    onClick={() => { setAuthMethod(\"otp\"); setError(\"\"); }}\n                    className={`flex-1 pb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-b-2 transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n                      authMethod === \"otp\"\n                        ? \"border-[#009DFF] text-white\"\n                        : \"border-transparent text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    Token Code (OTP)\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Form fields */}\n                <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                    <label className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest block font-bold\">\n                      Enterprise Email Address\n                    </label>\n                    <input\n                      type=\"email\"\n                      value={email}\n                      onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}\n                      placeholder=\"e.g. employee@gff.ai\"\n                      className=\"w-full h-10 px-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-950/80 border border-zinc-800 focus:border-[#009DFF] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF] text-zinc-100 text-xs placeholder-zinc-700 transition-all outline-none font-mono\"\n                      required\n                    />\n                  </div>\n\n                  {authMethod === \"credentials\" ? (\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest block font-bold\">\n                          Passphrase Key\n                        </label>\n                        <button\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => setShowForgot(true)}\n                          className=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-500 hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors focus:outline-none\"\n                        >\n                          Forgot Key?\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"relative\">\n                        <input\n                          type={showPassword ? \"text\" : \"password\"}\n                          value={password}\n                          onChange={(e) => setPassword(e.target.value)}\n                          placeholder=\"••••••••••••\"\n                          className=\"w-full h-10 pl-3 pr-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-950/80 border border-zinc-800 focus:border-[#009DFF] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF] text-zinc-100 text-xs placeholder-zinc-700 transition-all outline-none font-mono tracking-widest\"\n                          required\n                        />\n                        <button\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => setShowPassword(!showPassword)}\n                          className=\"absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors focus:outline-none\"\n                        >\n                          {showPassword ? <EyeOff className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> : <Eye className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />}\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  ) : (\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                        <label className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest block font-bold\">\n                          One-Time Passcode\n                        </label>\n                        <button\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => alert(\"OTP Token: Fill in any 6-digit passcode to run. Under local developer mode, this simulates multi-factor token authentication.\")}\n                          className=\"text-[9px] text-zinc-500 hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors focus:outline-none\"\n                        >\n                          Trouble sending?\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                      <input\n                        type=\"text\"\n                        value={otpCode}\n                        onChange={(e) => setOtpCode(e.target.value)}\n                        placeholder=\"102486\"\n                        maxLength={6}\n                        className=\"w-full h-10 px-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-950/80 border border-zinc-800 focus:border-[#009DFF] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF] text-zinc-100 text-xs placeholder-zinc-700 transition-all outline-none font-mono tracking-[0.4em] text-center\"\n                        required\n                      />\n                    </div>\n                  )}\n\n                  {error && (\n                    <div className=\"p-2.5 bg-red-950/40 border border-red-900/50 text-red-400 rounded-lg text-[11px] flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <AlertCircle className=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0\" />\n                      <span>{error}</span>\n                    </div>\n                  )}\n\n                  <button\n                    type=\"submit\"\n                    className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0086db] text-black font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer active:scale-[0.98] transition-all hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,157,255,0.15)]\"\n                  >\n                    <Lock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Initialize Secure Connection\n                  </button>\n                </form>\n\n                {/* SSO Button Placeholders */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 pt-2\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center text-[8.5px] text-zinc-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">\n                    <span className=\"h-[1px] bg-zinc-